# Refined Jump Action Consistency Plan

Addressing inconsistent jump behavior at platform gaps by unifying precision thresholds and refining navigation override logic.

## Root Cause Analysis

1.  **Threshold Conflict**: `MainForm's` jump logic requires a precision of 1.5px to trigger, but `CharacterMovementController's` movement logic considers any horizontal distance < 5.0px as "aligned" and stops moving. This causes the character to "stall" near jump points without actually jumping.
2.  **Aggressive Preservation**: Current [SelectNextTarget](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1117-1362) logic prioritizes original jump actions over rope navigation even when the character has fallen to a different level. This prevents the character from using ropes to recover and reach the jump point.
3.  **Landing Stability**: Characters sometimes advance waypoints immediately upon landing at the very edge of a platform, occasionally leading to falls during the subsequent movement.

## Proposed Changes

### [Core] [CharacterMovementController.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/CharacterMovementController.cs)
- [MODIFY] [MoveToTargetAsync](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/CharacterMovementController.cs#229-363): Change hardcoded `5.0` horizontal threshold to use `reachDistance`. Ensure a minimum threshold (e.g., 2.0) to prevent oscillation.

### [Core] [PathPlanningTracker.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs)
- [MODIFY] [SelectNextTarget](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1117-1362): Add a Y-axis check to the jump preservation logic. Only preserve the jump action if `Math.Abs(currentPos.Y - nextNode.Position.Y) < 15.0`. Otherwise, allow rope/A* navigation to handle recovery.

### [UI] [MainForm.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs)
- [MODIFY] [ProcessPathPlanning](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs#2690-2729) (Jump block): Add a short post-landing delay (e.g., 100ms) before calling [ForceAdvanceTarget](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1373-1418) to ensure stability.

